      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Your full name, home address, phone number, family members' names, and estimated income are probably sitting on dozens of websites right now — and you never put them there.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Data brokers scrape public records, social media, purchase histories, and court filings to build detailed profiles about you. They sell those profiles to marketers, insurers, and, unfortunately, scammers. If you've ever Googled yourself and found your info splashed across sites like Spokeo, BeenVerified, or WhitePages, you already know how unsettling that feels.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-optery"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Optery is a ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "data removal service",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " that handles the tedious, time-consuming process of contacting these brokers and demanding they delete your information. Instead of spending hours sending opt-out requests one by one, Optery automates the entire thing across hundreds of sites.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've tested this tool extensively, and in this tutorial, I'll walk you through exactly how to set it up, what to expect, and how to get the most out of it. Let's get your data off the web.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
