        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is Optery really free?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. The Basic plan is free forever and includes ongoing monitoring, a personalized exposure report with screenshots, and self-service opt-out guidance. No credit card is required to sign up.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How long does it take for Optery to remove my data?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Most removals are processed within a few days to a couple of weeks, depending on the broker. Some sites respond quickly; others take longer. Optery's dashboard tracks each request in real time so you always know the status.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can data brokers put my information back after Optery removes it?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes, this can happen because brokers continuously acquire new data. That's why Optery runs ongoing scans and automatically resubmits removal requests whenever your information reappears. This recurring protection is included in all paid plans.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Does Optery work outside the United States?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. Optery currently supports data removals in the US, Canada, Australia, New Zealand, and South Africa. If you have data in multiple countries, the service can handle removals across those regions.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
